quran[7{c,v,t}:
9,41,"tum subak-baar ho ya giran-baar ( yani maal o asbaab thora rakhtay ho ya bohat, gharon se ) nikal aao. aur khuda ke raste mein maal aur jaan se laro. yahi tumahray haq mein acha hai bashart e kay samjhoo"
9,42,agar mal-e ghanemat sahal al husool aur safar bhi halka sa hota to tumahray sath ( shoq se ) chal dete. lekin masafat un ko daur ( daraaz ) nazar aayi ( to izr karen ge ). aur khuda ki kasmain khayen ge ke agar hum taaqat rakhtay to aap ke sath zaroor nikal kharray hotay yeh ( aisay uzron se ) apne tain halaak kar rahay hain. aur khuda jaanta hai ke jhutay hain
9,43,khuda tumhe maaf kere. tum ne peshtar is ke ke tum par woh log bhi zahir ho jatay hain jo sachey hain aur woh bhi tumhe maloom ho jatay jo jhutay hain unn ko ijazat kyun di
9,44,jo log khuda par aur roz akhirat par imaan rakhtay hain woh to tum se ijazat nahi mangte ( ke peechay reh jayen balkay chahtay hain ke ) apne maal aur jaan se jehaad karen. aur khuda darny walon se waaqif hai
9,45,ijazat wohi log mangte hain jo khuda par aur pichlle din par imaan nahi rakhtay aur un ke dil shak mein parre hue hain. so woh apne shak mein danwaan doll ho rahay hain
9,46,aur agar woh niklny ka iradah karte hain to is ke liye samaan tayyar karte lekin khuda ne un ka uthna ( aur niklana ) pasand nahkiya to un ko hilnay julne hi nah diya aur ( un se ) keh diya gaya ke jahan ( mazoor ) baithy hain tum bhi un ke sath baithy raho
9,47,agar woh tum mein ( shaamil hokar ) nikal bhi kharray hotay to tumahray haq mein shararat karte aur tum mein fasaad dalwanay ki gharz se doray doray phirtay aur tum mein un ke jasoos bhi hain aur khuda zaalmon ko khoob jaanta hai
